title: Person hospitalized after crash through roadway barrier
text:
One person has been transported to Harborview -- after crashing into a jersey barrier on 164 th Street SW near I-5 in Lynnwood.
Lynnwood fire officials said a medical emergency caused the driver to travel through the barrier.
